-- Harmony Gold Says Second Body Is Recovered From Bambanani East Mine Shaft
-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 2010-09-30T05:00:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/harmony-gold-says-second-body-is-recovered-from-bambanani-east-mine-shaft.html
Harmony Gold Mining Ltd. said a
second body was recovered at its Bambanani East shaft following
a rockfall at the mine.  Three employees are being treated in the hospital after the
incident, the Randfontein-based company said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  